comments: Marshall (NOP) maintains a legal guarding position while contesting Durant's (BKN) shot attempt.
Valanciunas (NOP) and Claxton (BKN) mutually engage as both players come together during the rebound attempt. As they are disengaging,  Valanciunas slightly extends his arm into Claxton.
Warren (BKN) initiates contact with McCollum's (NOP) wrist as McCollum goes into his upward shooting motion.
Jones (NOP) moves alongside Durant's (BKN) path and avoids making contact with Durant's arm as he is gathering the ball into his shot attempt.
Murphy III (NOP) maintains a legal guarding position as Irving (BKN) splits two defenders during his drive toward the rim.
Durant (BKN) moves alongside McCollum's (NOP) path and maintains a legal guarding position during McCollum's drive toward the rim.
Claxton (BKN) jumps slightly forward and initiates marginal contact with Jones' (NOP) lower body during the shot attempt.
Simmons' (BKN) hand slides off McCollum's (NOP) off-arm as he moves to a vertical position during the shot attempt.
Jones (NOP) initiates contact to Claxton (BKN) that affects his ability to control the rebound.

As Irving (BKN) turns to run through the lane, he inadvertently makes contact with Alvarado's (NOP) head. Contact to an opponent's head/face can be deemed marginal when the result of a natural basketball move, provided the contact is not disproportionate or uncontrolled.
Jones (NOP) commits a take foul on Irving (BKN).
